dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Stearns County, Minnesota, C-10, Part B, Plate 10, Sensitivity of Ground-Water Systems to Pollution
dc_description_s: Map showing the susceptibility of the ground water system (bedrock and unconsolidated sediments) to contamination, including the age of the water as determined from radioactive isotopes in the water, scale 1:100,000, Stearns County.
dc_publisher_s: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters
